      • readPacket

        public void readPacket(net.minecraft.server.v1_8_R3.Packet<?> packet)
        Reads the incoming packet. Calls the PlayerInteractWithNPCEvent or the PlayerAttackNPCEvent if the packet is an instance of the PacketPlayInUseEntity.
        The PlayerInteractWithNPCEvent can be called every 0.3 seconds.
        The PlayerAttackNPCEvent can be called every half (0.5) seconds.
        Parameters:
        packet - the incoming packet
        Since:
        1.0
